		FOREACH. DEREF should eventually be propagated to other directives with
		'object' arguments, as well.
	
	+ Added exception-handling code to filterSyntaxTree() to filter off exceptions
		which appear in the syntax tree.
	
	/ Modified METHODCALL to allow mixed hash deref and method invocation in a
		single directive. This will allow methods to be invoked on objects within an
		array of hashrefs, for example.
	
