		should be fixed in Exception::ParamError.
	
	/ Fixed inconsistencies when dealing with subnodes. Was treating them sometimes
		like arrayrefs, and sometimes not.
	
	/ Fixed a bug in the way the results of a codeblock were dealt with. Codeblocks
		can now return a list without fear of it being used in scalar context.
	
